    <p>Stay­ing home be­cause the usual Christ­mas par­ties have been can­celled this year?</p>
    <p>You can still get into the Yule­tide spirit by div­ing onto the sofa and into these new Christ­mas-themed en­ter­tain­ment of­fer­ings.</p>
    <p>From fes­tive songs by mu­sic stars such as Mariah Carey and feel-good movies star­ring Goldie Hawn to com­edy skits by coun­try mu­sic star Chris Stapleton and a char­ity drive by Sin­ga­pore artists, here are 10 of­fer­ings you can stream on­line or watch on tele­vi­sion.</p>

